import React from 'react';
import { AppBar, Button, Toolbar, Typography, Link} from '@mui/material'
import MedicalServicesIcon from '@mui/icons-material/MedicalServices';
import ShoppingCartSharpIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ShoppingCartSharp';
const Header = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <AppBar position="sticky" elevation={0}>
                <Toolbar>
                    <MedicalServicesIcon />
                    <Typography sx={{ padding: "10px" }}>Welcome to Med/Pharma</Typography>
                    <Link>
                        <Link href="#">
                            Home
                        </Link>
                        <Link href="#" underline="hover">
                            About
                        </Link>
                        <Link href="#" underline="always">
                            Contact
                        </Link>
                    </Link>
                    {/* <Tabs textColor='1px solid white'>
                            <Tab label="Home" />
                            <Tab label="About" />
                            <Tab label="Contact Us" />
                        </Tabs> */}
                    <Button variant="contained" sx={{ marginLeft: "37rem" }}>Login</Button>
                    <ShoppingCartSharpIcon sx={{ marginLeft: "auto" }} />
                </Toolbar>
            </AppBar>
        </React.Fragment>

    )
}

export default Header
